{"data":[{"date":"10:15 01/08","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lazio chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao Savic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/24/chu-tich-lazio-chia-se-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-ngoi-sao-savic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, khi ph\u00eda Lazio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Savic.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMilinkovic-Savic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00fap C1 Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Man United c\u00f9ng Juventus \u1edf Serie A l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng CLB r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Sergej Milinkivic-Savic c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia, v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Cho d\u00f9 Lazio kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng Savic v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1eadn t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lazio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/muc-tieu-tri-gia-100-trieu-euro-cua-mu-muon-gia-nhap-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lazio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a CLB Lazio &ndash; \u00f4ng Claudio Lotito c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Milinkovic-Savic, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng xem x\u00e9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi mua n\u00e0o. Sau Juventus, Inter v\u00e0 Milan, Lazio c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Italia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t danh hi\u1ec7u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; ph\u00eda Lazio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Savic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111\u00e3 ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A, gi\u00fap Lazio c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real: T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i &ldquo;c\u1eeda t\u1eed&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Man United s\u1ebd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4920","checkdouble":"192444"},{"date":"10:34 01/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/inter-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u01b0a tin Inter Milan \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Luka Modric \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia t\u1edbi Giuseppe Meazza ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Modric ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 43 tr\u1eadn cho Real Madrid m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng quang danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018. Anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng Vatreni l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-vat/luka-modric-ngon-co-dau-cua-nguoi-croatia-389-190104.html\" target=\"_blank\">Luka Modric</span> gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric c\u1ee7a Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric c\u1ee7a Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Inter-muon-chieu-mo-Modric-cua-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Inter mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric c\u1ee7a Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Sky Sports, Inter \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Nerazzurri s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Champions League l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 6 n\u0103m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Serie A \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real nh\u1ea3 Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Inter l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Modric \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. Marcelo Brozovic, Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 Sime Vrsaljko \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Inter \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo. \u201cK\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng\u201d kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa nh\u01b0 Modric. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham v\u1ecdng, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0o tho\u00e1t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard-180-192441.html\">CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4919","checkdouble":"192453"},{"date":"11:01 01/08","title":"Mourinho: \"Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mourinho-chien-thang-truoc-real-chang-co-y-nghia-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, nh\u01b0ng Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec1u ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa M.U vs Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1edfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, thay v\u00ec tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Ander Herrera l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Karim Benzema g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 1 b\u00e0n cho K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u1ea3. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Herrera, Bailly, Mata, Darmian, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi thi \u0111\u00e2\u00ed m\u1ecdi ph\u00fat trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec v\u1eady trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eafng 2-1, h\u00f2a 2-2, thua 1-2 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, ch\u1eb3ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid\" title=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/mourinho-chien-thang-truoc-real-chang-co-y-nghia-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 cho CLB v\u00ec ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c khi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Real Madrid 1-6, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd th\u1eadt phi th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Herrera, Mata v\u00e0 Sanchez, h\u1ecd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh trong 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c v\u1eabn mang theo Kroos, Asensio, Isco.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y &lsquo;xong&rsquo; r\u1ed3i, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Premier League, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec3 xua tan s\u1ee9c \u00e9p trong th\u1eddi gian qua. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi Real &ndash; CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i v\u00ec M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo; &ndash; Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real: T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i &ldquo;c\u1eeda t\u1eed&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Man United s\u1ebd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4918","checkdouble":"192458"},{"date":"11:45 01/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-rua-mat-cua-mu-truoc-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Sanchez\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t MU 2-1 Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t MU 2-1 Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/4-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-rua-mat-MU-2-1-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sanchez n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i ICC b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t tour \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 lao \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt th\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sanchez h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t, HLV Mourinho t\u1eebng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo sau m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00edch nghi \u1edf Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 l\u1eddi ti\u00ean \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u1ee9ng nghi\u1ec7m, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Sanchez th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc b\u00e9n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Real, Sanchez ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 b\u1eb1ng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c. Sau \u0111\u00f3 anh c\u00f3 pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i cho Herrera ghi b\u00e0n n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Sanchez ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Hard Rock v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Herrera v\u00e0 Mata \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera\" title=\"Herrera\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Herrera s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t cho MU m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng t\u1edbi 17 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i h\u1eadu World Cup. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Mourinho ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ea l\u1ebft qua chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSanchez l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. Nh\u01b0ng Ander Herrera v\u00e0 Juan Mata l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Man United. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League c\u1ee7a MU sau \u0111\u00e2y 1 tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Mourinho. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u, Herrera v\u00e0 Mata s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u00ecn gi\u1eef hy v\u1ecdng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU v\u1eabn nhi\u1ec1u s\u01a1 h\u1edf\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fosu-Mensah\" title=\"Fosu-Mensah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/114149-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU 2-1 Real Madrid</span> v\u1eeba qua nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. V\u00ec b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 ra sao th\u00ec Mourinho v\u1eabn \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Benzema v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Bailly v\u00e0 McTominay \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh tung l\u01b0\u1edbi De Gea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Bailly, McTominay v\u00e0 Fosu-Mensah. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi ch\u01a1i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Chris Smalling ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Phil Jones v\u00e0 Marcos Rojo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u00ec Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Fred c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fred\" title=\"Fred\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fred x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Liverpool t\u1ea1i Michigan. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Real m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Tuy kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Fred gi\u00fap \u00edch cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111en duy nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Fred l\u00e0 pha m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba MU. R\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t Ceballos tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Real k\u1ecbp d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Fellaini ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nemanja Matic v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c sau ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt, Fred nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester sau \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n 1 tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mourinho-chien-thang-truoc-real-chang-co-y-nghia-gi-184-192458.html\">Mourinho: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4917","checkdouble":"192465"},{"date":"09:44 01/08","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real: T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i \u201cc\u1eeda t\u1eed\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Man United s\u1ebd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 l\u1ecdc l\u00f5i c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Mou United&rdquo;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, Man United \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd h\u00f2a Club America 1-1, h\u00f2a San Jose Earthquakes 0-0, h\u00f2a Milan 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thua \u0111\u1eadm Liverpool 1-4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, M.U \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0 Fred hay David De Gea m\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m MU 2-1 Real T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i c\u1eeda t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m MU 2-1 Real T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i c\u1eeda t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Du-am-MU-2-1-Real-Tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Fred</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n &ldquo;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho M.U tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn kh\u00e1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea. Ngay c\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t Mourinho. \u00d4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 k\u1ebb d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 n\u00e0o, song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 Mou c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh s\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U the hien bo mat khac truoc Real\" title=\"M.U the hien bo mat khac truoc Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/M.U-the-hien-bo-mat-khac-truoc-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, Real v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 M.U hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Mourinho, B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u00f2n c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi h\u01a1n 70%, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. \u0110\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0ng nh\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i La Liga, Real c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a M.U n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. X\u00e9t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1, &ldquo;Mou United&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec1u thua k\u00e9m Real. Nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, xem M.U kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u00edch m\u1eaft, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Song kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192425.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/mu-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192425.html\">MU 2-1 Real Madrid (KT): Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n nh\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Sanchez</span><br>\r\n<span>V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ph\u00fat 18, Juan Mata ch\u1ecdc khe th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u1ec3 Darmian b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u0103ng ngang t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e1 n\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 27, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tam gi\u00e1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c. Mata t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng, Sanchez \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m cho Ander Herrera volley r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho M.U. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U danh bai Real 2-1 tai My\" title=\"M.U danh bai Real 2-1 tai My\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/M.U-danh-bai-Real-2-1-tai-My.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real mang \u0111\u1eadm phong c\u00e1ch HLV&nbsp;Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Karim Benzema ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh an \u1ee7i cho Real. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U lu\u00f4n v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 chung cu\u1ed9c th\u1eafng 2-1. \u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay v\u00ec con s\u1ed1 g\u1ea5p 3, 4 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i cho M.U l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Real Madrid. S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n sau 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0 \u00fd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Hard Rock, Florida.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 non n\u1edbt c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Ti\u1ec3u k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018, HLV Julen Lopetegui quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea3 l\u1ecfng. C\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng U21 v\u00e0 \u0110TQG T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vinicius Junior cua Real\" title=\"Vinicius Junior cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Vinicius-Junior-cua-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Real nh\u01b0 Vinicius ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng &ldquo;Ti\u1ec3u k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n&rdquo; t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChung cu\u1ed9c, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Real l\u00ean t\u1edbi 71%. H\u1ecd tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh M.U song ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u00e0 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t cho Real tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Benzema v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m sau qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Theo Hernandez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema ghi ban cho Real\" title=\"Benzema ghi ban cho Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Benzema-ghi-ban-cho-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00fa \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Benzema l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Real l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Benzema t\u1ea1o ra. D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Gareth Bale. H\u1ecd v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh M.U c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t. Real c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1 an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Real thi\u1ebfu \u0111i nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn, s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf 1/3 cu\u1ed1i s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Los Blancos th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u1edb Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i Bale, Benzema g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u1eefng Isco, Kroos hay Asensio ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf h\u01a1n 10 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Real B ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o, m\u1ed9t trung phong bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test m\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i. Qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi M.U, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd l\u1ecdc ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 h\u1eefu \u00edch cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1 m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH XU\u1ea4T PH\u00c1T:<br>\r\nMan United (4-4-1-1):</strong> David de Gea; Matteo Darmian, Eric Bailly, Timothy Fosu-Mensah, Luke Shaw; Fred, Ander Herrera, Scott McTominay, Andreas Pereira; Juan Mata, Alexis Sanchez.<br>\r\n<strong>Real Madrid (4-2-3-1):</strong> Kiko Casilla; Alvaro Odriozola, Jesus Vallejo, Javier Sanchez, Theo Hernandez; Marcos Llorente, Federico Valverde; Vinicius, Gareth Bale, Daniel Ceballos; Karim Benzema.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u  MU 2-1 Real (ICC 2018):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/Mu-2-1-real.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4916","checkdouble":"192450"},{"date":"10:23 01/08","title":"Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 5 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa m\u1edbi m\u01a1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/man-utd-can-them-5-tan-binh-nua-moi-mo-canh-tranh-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Charlie Adam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 3 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i bom t\u1ea5n Fred, hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 bao g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ch\u01b0a ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ea7n mua th\u00eam 5 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ea7n mua th\u00eam 5 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/man-utd-can-them-5-tan-binh-nua-moi-mo-canh-tranh-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ea7n mua th\u00eam 5 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng l\u1ea5y g\u00ec l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Real Madrid</span>. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i trong 90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, Charlie Adam t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 bi quan khi nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a MU. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool tin r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, n\u00f3i: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;N\u0103m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Trong \u0111\u00f3 quan tr\u1ecdng, m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i, m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao v\u00ec l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho Alexis Sanchez, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Ngay c\u1ea3 Romelu Lukaku c\u0169ng n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00eda sau.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Bayern Munich, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City \u1edf Old Trafford t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u ng\u00e0y 10/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4915","checkdouble":"192454"},{"date":"10:54 01/08","title":"B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd t\u00ednh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/bi-mourinho-thuc-giuc-dan-cau-thu-man-utd-cat-ngan-ky-nghi-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcus Rashford, Phil Jones,... v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd kh\u00e1c \u0111ang t\u00ednh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 sau l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e2n v\u00ec c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup, Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Theo Independent, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/bi-mourinho-thuc-giuc-dan-cau-thu-man-utd-cat-ngan-ky-nghi-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup v\u00ec Mourinho.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Ruben Loftus-Cheek c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. Bernardo Silva c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City s\u1edbm khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Man Utd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Romelu Lukaku, Paul Pogba, Ashley Young,...<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i lo v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p Anh, m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ngh\u1ec9 \"t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 tu\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 tu\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp\". Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (FIFPro) b\u00e0y t\u1ecf lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 trong n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">FIFPro tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 lo ng\u1ea1i: \"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n, b\u1ecb k\u1eb9t gi\u1eefa l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. FIFPro hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Champions League v\u00e0 Europa League t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">FIFPro hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00e0nh lang \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 4 tu\u1ea7n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n gi\u1eefa tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, cho \u0111\u1ebfn bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Man Utd h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-can-them-5-tan-binh-nua-moi-mo-canh-tranh-vo-dich-172-192454.html\">Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 5 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa m\u1edbi m\u01a1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo-172-192380.html\">T\u00e2n binh Man Utd tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Mourinho x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-co-nguy-co-bi-sa-thai-cao-nhat-tai-premier-league-172-192349.html\">Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd-184-192346.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 30/7: Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u nh\u00f3m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-307-187-192302.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 30/7: Man Utd ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n Martial cho PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau-172-192298.html\">Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4914","checkdouble":"192455"},{"date":"10:55 01/08","title":"PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao s\u00e1ng Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/psg-chua-tu-bo-kante.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, Les Parisiens v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a anh h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u00ednh tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n Kante</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, N'Golo Kante l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Leicester City, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKante g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong 2 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA c\u1ee7a Chelsea 2 m\u00f9a qua. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, Kante c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/PSG-chua-tu-bo-Kante,-nha-vo-dich-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Kante</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Kante, Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 290 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n, m\u1ee9c cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG ch\u01b0a b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u1eef ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea, PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1eadu thu\u1eabn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Qatar, \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuoi cung thi Kante cung duoc thoai mai tao dang voi chiec cup ma khong con phai ben len nho ban muon ho.\" title=\"Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec Kante c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ebdn l\u1ebdn nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/deschamps-can-loi-khi-kante-xuong-phong-do-o-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch WC\u00a02018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Thomas Tuchel t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Kante c\u1ee7a PSG. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m d\u00e0nh cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, PSG m\u1edbi chia tay l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Thiago Motta v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Adrien Rabiot ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch ra \u0111i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Barcelona. \u1ede ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Lassana Diarra l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i th\u00ec nh\u1eefng Lo Celso hay Yacine Adli l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard-180-192441.html\">CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-khung-cua-mu-va-chelsea-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192422.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-172-192406.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-khien-real-van-chua-the-cong-bo-bom-tan-courtois-172-192377.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid-172-192368.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4913","checkdouble":"192456"},{"date":"11:13 01/08","title":"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U, th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \"kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Martial \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin vui bu\u1ed3n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Real Madrid trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9, Man United \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Ander Herrera l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Benzema \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M.U v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, khi h\u1ecd t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 World Cup 2018. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 Anthony Martial li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Anh \u0111\u00e3 xin ph\u00e9p CLB v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 &ldquo;h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00ea&rdquo;, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m quay l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Martial s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real\" title=\"MU 2-1 Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin t\u00edch c\u1ef1c: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League trong 9 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Victor Lindelof &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ngo\u00e0i ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 Rashford, Jones v\u00e0 Lukaku &ndash; nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn 3 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u1edf trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 theo c\u00e1ch t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00e0 ch\u1edd Lindelof, Rasford, Lukaku v\u00e0 Jones tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n ngay, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n. Trong kho\u1ea3ng 2-3 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Premier League&rdquo; &ndash; Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mourinho-chien-thang-truoc-real-chang-co-y-nghia-gi-184-192458.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mourinho-chien-thang-truoc-real-chang-co-y-nghia-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mourinho-chien-thang-truoc-real-chang-co-y-nghia-gi-184-192458.html\">Mourinho: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, nh\u01b0ng Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real: T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i &ldquo;c\u1eeda t\u1eed&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Man United s\u1ebd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4912","checkdouble":"192459"},{"date":"11:45 01/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh cho r\u1eb1ng M.U s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Man City \u1edf EPL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/truyen-thong-anh-cho-rang-mu-se-can-duong-man-city-o-epl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, chuy\u00ean gia Graeme Souness c\u1ee7a Sky Sports nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Man City.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sir Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u, v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Graeme Souness cho r\u1eb1ng Man United ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Man City. K\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 100 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Mourinho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Souness chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Man City h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 m\u1ecdi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ngai v\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Man United s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eadp tan v\u00e0o ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sky Sports nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sky Sports nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/114250-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sky Sports nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, cho r\u1eb1ng M.U s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Liverpool s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Jurgen Klopp. Chelsea, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Hazard &ndash; Courtois, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu Tottenham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00f4i sao, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 Man City s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&rdquo; &ndash; chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a Sky Sports nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u tu\u1ea7n sau (11/8), v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Leicester City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau-172-192459.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau-172-192459.html\">Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U, th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Martial \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin vui bu\u1ed3n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-man-city-chieu-mo-them-mot-tan-binh-172-192434.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-man-city-chieu-mo-them-mot-tan-binh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-man-city-chieu-mo-them-mot-tan-binh-172-192434.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh</span><br>\r\nMan City mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Philippe Sandler, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chot-gia-ban-day-bat-ngo-cho-joe-hart-172-192394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/6/man-city-chot-gia-ban-day-bat-ngo-cho-joe-hart.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chot-gia-ban-day-bat-ngo-cho-joe-hart-172-192394.html\">Man City ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Joe Hart</span><br>\r\nMan City b\u00e1n Joe Hart v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Pep Guardiola \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4911","checkdouble":"192464"},{"date":"07:09 01/08","title":"CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb b\u1ecf k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</h2><h2>CLB Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Christian-Pulisic-voi-gia-70-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ph\u00eda Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf v\u1ee5 Hazard</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Ronaldo chia tay Real, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Eden Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Ba\u0309n th\u00e2n Eden Hazard cu\u0303ng ba\u0300y to\u0309 y\u0301 \u0111i\u0323nh gia nh\u00e2\u0323p Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o ng\u00f5 c\u1ee5t. T\u01a1\u0300 El Pais m\u01a1\u0301i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111a\u0303 ti\u00ea\u0301t l\u00f4\u0323 Los Blancos \u0111a\u0303 s\u0103\u0303n sa\u0300ng t\u01b0\u0300 bo\u0309 th\u01b0\u01a1ng vu\u0323 na\u0300y. Theo ba\u0301o chi\u0301 T\u00e2y Ban Nha,\u00a0K\u00ea\u0300n K\u00ea\u0300n Tr\u0103\u0301ng kh\u00f4ng s\u0103\u0303n sa\u0300ng \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u00f4\u0323t m\u01b0\u0301c gia\u0301 ky\u0309 lu\u0323c cho c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 ng\u01b0\u01a1\u0300i Bi\u0309.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea t\u1eebng ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Hi\u1ec7n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang co\u0301 y\u0301 \u0111i\u0323nh trao chi\u00ea\u0301c b\u0103ng thu\u0309 qu\u00e2n cho Eden Hazard. B\u0103ng \u0111\u00f4\u0323i tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0309ng cu\u0309a The Blues \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c n\u0103\u0301m gi\u01b0\u0303 b\u01a1\u0309i trung v\u00ea\u0323 Gary Cahill.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Real, HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u0169ng \u0111ang ti\u0301nh \u0111\u00ea\u0301n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng a\u0301n kha\u0301c n\u00ea\u0301u kh\u00f4ng th\u00ea\u0309 chi\u00eau m\u00f4\u0323 Eden Hazard. Ca\u0301c ba\u0301o cho bi\u00ea\u0301t, HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111a\u0303 g\u01b0\u0309i m\u00f4\u0323t ba\u0309n danh sa\u0301ch nh\u01b0\u0303ng ca\u0301i t\u00ean c\u00e2\u0300n mua cho ban la\u0303nh \u0111a\u0323o Los Blancos. Theo \u0111o\u0301, c\u01b0\u0323u thuy\u00ea\u0300n tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0309ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00e2\u0300n th\u00eam m\u00f4\u0323t trung v\u00ea\u0323, m\u00f4\u0323t ti\u00ea\u0300n v\u00ea\u0323 va\u0300 m\u00f4\u0323t ti\u00ea\u0300n \u0111a\u0323o.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo-184-192440.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo-184-192440.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/8: Sao Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nSao Real mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Pochettino \u201c\u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y\u201d Mourinho, \u2018H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 Barca mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp M.U,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund-180-192424.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/9/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund-180-192424.html\">T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Dortmund</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Pulisic, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4910","checkdouble":"192441"},{"date":"08:12 01/08","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo \u1edf \u00dd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-nguoi-hung-world-cup-se-doi-dau-ronaldo-o-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Sime Vrsaljko t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sime Vrsaljko l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia</span>. T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf Atletico Madrid nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-nguoi-hung-world-cup-se-doi-dau-ronaldo-o-y.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi HLV Diego Simeone, Vrsaljko ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. \u0110\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u201cthu\u00ea\u201d ng\u00f4i sao Croatia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 6,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro, k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t b\u1eb1ng 17,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 Atletico Madrid: \u201cCLB ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Inter Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Sime Vrsaljko. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cSau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 hy sinh cho CLB, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fac Sime m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ti\u1ebfp theo \u1edf Inter. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mua \u0111\u1ee9t sau \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ea5t Vrsaljko nh\u01b0ng Atletico c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Santiago Arias. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Wanda Metropolitano t\u1eeb PSV Eindhoven v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga-187-192018.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chinh-thuc-them-mot-ngoi-sao-cap-ben-la-liga-187-192018.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn La Liga</span><br>\r\nCLB Atletico Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Gelson Martins t\u1eeb CLB Sporting Lisbon...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4909","checkdouble":"192442"},{"date":"08:47 01/08","title":"Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/22/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i im h\u01a1i l\u1eb7ng ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, trong khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\" target=\"_blank\">si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng Neymar, Kylian Mbappe, Eden Hazard hay Harry Kane \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League t\u00ednh \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d b\u1eb1ng Robert Lewandowski, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i khi m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Bayern Munich nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u201cH\u00f9m X\u00e1m x\u1ee9 Bavaria\u201d trong th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 70: \u201cV\u1edbi Robert, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i CLB, r\u1eb1ng Bayern Munich l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu m\u1ed7i khi m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd m\u1edf c\u1eeda ra v\u00ec n\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 Robert trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 100 hay 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, Robert v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: Hazard s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, nh\u01b0ng thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo? Kh\u00f4ng!</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n cung 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a khi Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juventus, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4908","checkdouble":"192443"}]}